{"tid":87921,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"問條英文閱讀理解題","createTime":"2017-01-20T08:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T16:39:22.000Z","uid":44592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ddd23707a9dc60a12191964fda3cb6e25c07c33","tid":87921,"uid":44592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"原句為<br />\n<br />\nEating till 3pm, then continue drinking alone.<br />\n<br />\n以上句子，是否必定理解為<br />\n<br />\n三點之前一路飲一路食，之後只係淨飲唔食。<br />\n<br />\n注意，我重點為 是否必解。謝謝連登仔解答[/quote]"},{"pid":"dc0878aecb32815944a3bca9a2ae1311b306170d","tid":87921,"uid":44592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原句為<br />\n<br />\nEating till 3pm, then continue drinking alone.<br />\n<br />\n以上句子，是否必定理解為<br />\n<br />\n三點之前一路飲一路食，之後只係淨飲唔食。<br />\n<br />\n注意，我重點為 <span style=\"color: red;\">是否必定理解</span>。謝謝連登仔解答</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ff271b7bbc1570acffc4cb8c2c7f63a90cb2002c","tid":87921,"uid":56408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"2222ac979da56670518e03ca9f369e63dbcede14","tid":87921,"uid":16607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"前面應該係3點前可以飲食<br />\n之後只可以飲"},{"pid":"5dcbb0e0b2bdd55dc19e148f82fbf10dfdb473a2","tid":87921,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:15:19.000Z","msg":"無一定.<br />\n<br />\n個人理解 :<br />\nEating 指食/進餐.<br />\n進餐至下午3時, 隨後時間繼續留下喝飲料"},{"pid":"b93b9608c3900be94a4c56fc039d3081cf9f898b","tid":87921,"uid":44592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"Okay,  咁我轉一轉字眼，望下是否相同結果。<br />\n<br />\nDrug A till Monday, then continue Drug B alone.<br />\n<br />\n大家理解會否有唔同，有的話係因為咩原因。<br />\n最好有人講下以grammar 角度講應該點樣解釋。"},{"pid":"bd4a6617f7e5c983e2d3ddae0ee9d17e6a22f485","tid":87921,"uid":69679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"Alone VS only<br />\n<br />\nAlone 解自己一個wor, 兩回事<br />\n<br />\nOnly 就解只係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c54b203ab6b1227ef2cd4eff28b3dd3ec2c05a","tid":87921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Alone VS only<br />\n<br />\nAlone 解自己一個wor, 兩回事<br />\n<br />\nOnly 就解只係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAlone 可以解only"},{"pid":"fe7ec57cd810747b43de604232a1edddf410ad1e","tid":87921,"uid":69679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Alone VS only<br />\n<br />\nAlone 解自己一個wor, 兩回事<br />\n<br />\nOnly 就解只係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAlone 可以解only</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係usage問題, 你寫alone, reader第一時間即刻解作單獨飲酒，你將alone解only完全有ambiguity, 鬼佬根本唔會有only唔用，走去用alone"},{"pid":"4334cb742cb653936c709265770a4e897f6e2622","tid":87921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Alone VS only<br />\n<br />\nAlone 解自己一個wor, 兩回事<br />\n<br />\nOnly 就解只係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAlone 可以解only</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係usage問題, 你寫alone, reader第一時間即刻解作單獨飲酒，你將alone解only完全有ambiguity, 鬼佬根本唔會有only唔用，走去用alone</blockquote><br />\n不過樓上drug個題，alone係幾合理bor"},{"pid":"0f0872780e42aea4d9278e34c28c654c046fa51b","tid":87921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"重點係「continue」<br />\n<br />\n-&gt; 前後兩句既動作/行為要有一致性<br />\n<br />\nDrug個題，可以解做服用A藥療程到星期一；之後繼續單服用B藥<br />\n-&gt; 無一定要同時用A,B藥<br />\n<br />\n進食個題，可以解做進餐時間段到三點；之後只供飲用"},{"pid":"59fc79456798dd60423b153329c820294834c96d","tid":87921,"uid":44592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重點係「continue」<br />\n<br />\n-&amp;gt; 前後兩句既動作/行為要有一致性<br />\n<br />\nDrug個題，可以解做服用A藥療程到星期一；之後繼續單服用B藥<br />\n-&amp;gt; 無一定要同時用A,B藥<br />\n<br />\n進食個題，可以解做進餐時間段到三點；之後只供飲用</blockquote><br />\n即係以grammar 來睇，藥果面都係先a後b而不是a and b then b,right?"},{"pid":"f07a55dcae755a5c499cb5eed4df6b471958217e","tid":87921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>重點係「continue」<br />\n<br />\n-&amp;amp;gt; 前後兩句既動作/行為要有一致性<br />\n<br />\nDrug個題，可以解做服用A藥療程到星期一；之後繼續單服用B藥<br />\n-&amp;amp;gt; 無一定要同時用A,B藥<br />\n<br />\n進食個題，可以解做進餐時間段到三點；之後只供飲用</blockquote><br />\n即係以grammar 來睇，藥果面都係先a後b而不是a and b then b,right?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，因為句子無明確表達a,b同時食既關係<br />\n<br />\n可以assume 有 drug a,b,c,d,e...<br />\n<br />\n先食a, 再單服b(從句子只可以直接推：b藥不會與a混合，that's all)"},{"pid":"28ec8c0608c3d3b1295094ec0242b8c9e68823f9","tid":87921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"但eating , drinking 明顯兩個唔同行為<br />\n-&gt; 以continue駁兩句<br />\n-&gt; 似係想表達想繼續係同一個「地方」飲埋佢"},{"pid":"2360a9aa59b095a45a5ea903fc8151e05c892e0a","tid":87921,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"咁點解alone一定係指drinking，而唔可以係指個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137a45646700b21a328b910ea3b9941091f1eaa1","tid":87921,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解alone一定係指drinking，而唔可以係指個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話唔得，但就推唔到前一句會同時eating and drinking <br />\n-&gt; 呢個先係句子重點"},{"pid":"438a425f26edad7f8332f1c2d8d9a4f230886e33","tid":87921,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁點解alone一定係指drinking，而唔可以係指個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話唔得，但就推唔到前一句會同時eating and drinking <br />\n-&amp;gt; 呢個先係句子重點</blockquote><br />\n我諗正常人見到drinking alone都諗係自己一個飲酒掛"}]}